text: Superman is the third studio album by the Swedish-Iranian Arash (full name Arash Labaf) after self-titled Arash in 2005 and Donya in 2008. The singles from the album include "Broken Angel", "Melody", "Iran Iran World Cup 2014", "She Makes Me Go" featuring Sean Paul, "Sex Love Rock n Roll (SLR)" featuring T-Pain. ==Track listing== #"One Day" (3:32) #"Sex Love Rock n Roll (SLR)" (2:57) #"Tekoon Bede" (2:39) #"Superman" (3:31) #"Ba Man Soot Bezan" (3:31) #"She Makes Me Go" (2:58) #"Doga Doga" (3:16) #"Ma Bala" (3:11) #"Delhore" (3:20) #"Melody" (3:12) #"Broken Angel" (3:12) #"Che Konam" (3:04) #"On Est La" (3:02) #"Boro Boro" (2:56) #"Sex Love Rock n Roll (SLR) (Basshunter Remix) (3:49) #"One Day" (Golden Star Mix) (3:00) #"Iran Iran World Cup 2014" (3:14) Category:2014 albums Category:Arash (singer) albums Category:2000s pop album stubs
